{
  "stem": "12904.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He tried to intervene on behalf of someone he knew who was taken to a concentration camp, and was trying to intervene, and to have this man released.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was told, in no uncertain terms, to-- to leave the thing alone and not to interfere.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he was still practicing in some very limited way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know exactly what he-- what kind of law where he didn't have to go to court or so.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But by '35, it was certainly obvious that he couldn't make a living anymore.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "See?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I see.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So in the interim then, you have gone to England.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What were the circumstances?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to England because I could no longer attend school, high school, in Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I actually had only one more year, you know, to finish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we decided, my cousin-- the one who later committed suicide-- that we would go together.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was a year and a half older.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I was 17, she was but 18 and 1/2.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we would go and-- well, I spent a few weeks with a family outside of London in Petersfield, where the girl, the daughter, had been a guest with us in Germany for, I think, in the-- during the summer, months at one time.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so I was there first, and I realized that I wasn't getting anywhere.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, I wasn't getting an education anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we both, my cousin and I, applied to the new school, it's a Steiner school, which I had attended briefly in Germany, too.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And for fixing high tea-- it's a boarding school-- for fixing high tea every day and doing some babysitting for the teacher who owned the home, owned the school, and his wife, we were able to attend classes with the other students.",
      "word_count": 42
    }
  ],
